# Environment Variables for TongHopTinTuc

# Required for AI content generation
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Required for Facebook posting
FB_PAGE_ID=your_facebook_page_id
FB_TOKEN=your_facebook_access_token

# Optional for Telegram notifications
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=your_telegram_chat_id

# Required for Reddit API access (Reddit Integration Phase 08)
# Format: platform:app_id:version (by /u/username)
# Example: nodejs:tonghoptintuc:v1.1 (by /u/yourusername)
REDDIT_USER_AGENT=nodejs:tonghoptintuc:v1.1 (by /u/yourusername)

## Reddit User-Agent Setup
# Reddit requires a descriptive User-Agent header for API access.
# Replace 'yourusername' with your actual Reddit username.
# If not set, a default value will be used (not recommended for production).
